All very hush-hush.

39
00:03:42.960 --> 00:03:44.039
What are they?

40
00:03:44.040 --> 00:03:46.439
He likes his hot
chocolate with marshmallows on.

41
00:03:46.440 --> 00:03:49.519
You must mean business.
Never done them before.

42
00:03:49.520 --> 00:03:52.480
